        </section>
        <p data-uuid="b8e35fabb1f2432fa43c28f048af8a56">Over live radio, Darrow and Bryan attacked each other’s ideas. After more than a week on trial, Scopes was convicted and fined $100 for breaking the law. The state supreme court later overturned his conviction, but the debate over evolution continued.</p>
